{"tid":1671652,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"杯葛加泰集會！","createTime":"2019-10-23T15:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T15:28:43.000Z","uid":181655,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"49ad759fb6ca38b16f25cd2dec82243361d5a041","tid":1671652,"uid":181655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"我地要國際勢力支持就吾好掂呢舊<br />\n豬頭骨！<br />\n加獨連美帝歐盟都反對之時，香港人死去支持做咩？<br />\n甚至吾排除加泰人都只系想利用香港黎沾光渣！<br />\n連人地的企圖都吾知去聲援人！<br />\n我地反警暴？<br />\n就算用咩名目都好一定會俾人覺得同加泰勾連<br />\n以後香港有咩問題即刻就提加泰禁點算？<br />\n重有點解今次有不反對通知書？<br />\n會吾會系陰謀？<br />\n我地系抗爭者吾系耶和華，無論幾同情人都好請放在心中，吾好行動支持呀！希望各位審慎考慮"},{"pid":"21dc48282c0310aeb7e45eaad6ee63c1a64e1a1b","tid":1671652,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:21:29.000Z","msg":"突發 有人想自廢武功 全世界入嚟幫拖啊！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671611</a>"},{"pid":"dc5135e1b4660df4a1d1b509a6852bb8ae57722c","tid":1671652,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:21:58.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"184fed8f606d262c1b887b58c2edcf7f7f841299","tid":1671652,"uid":314130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"dfa8d8ae5c7fa39c3981a6047e1b63a5d2ffb39e","tid":1671652,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"4f7e3dbd371dd978360db647daefe4e4db7d3966","tid":1671652,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"屌 你咪杯囉 做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登只係宣傳渠道唔係大台 又無人逼你去<br />\n<br />\n撐警集會又唔見你喺度開po話杯葛？"},{"pid":"960fe9b5dd1eda89baa9682dc84af66e7f6f8781","tid":1671652,"uid":181655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f7e3dbd371dd978360db647daefe4e4db7d3966","tid":1671652,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT